               <code codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" code="34069-5" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Meclizine hydrochloride tablets, USP are available in the following strengths:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>12.5 mg (Blue, oval shaped tablets, debossed with “TL 122” with score on one side and plain on the other side.)</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>25 mg (Yellow, oval shaped tablets, debossed with “TL 121” with score on one side and plain on the other side.)</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>They are supplied by <content styleCode="bold"> DOH CENTRAL PHARMACY</content> as follows:</paragraph>
                  <table width="100%">
                     <colgroup>
                        <col width="13%"/>
                        <col width="25%"/>
                        <col width="25%"/>
                        <col width="25%"/>
                        <col width="12%"/>
                     </colgroup>
                     <thead>
